  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for ceph",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for ceph to version ceph-12.2.5-419-g8cbf63d997 fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2018-10861: Ensure that ceph-mon does perform authorization on all OSD pool ops (bsc#1099162).\n- CVE-2018-1129: cephx signature check bypass (bsc#1096748).\n- CVE-2018-1128: cephx protocol was vulnerable to replay attack (bsc#1096748).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
